cs.DB, cs.LO, cs.CC, cs.AI, cs.DS 

This paper deals with the dynamic complexity of conjunctive queries, which is a topic closely related to databases and data management. Therefore, cs.DB is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves logical reasoning and complexity analysis, which suggests cs.LO and cs.CC as likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the impact of additional operators and features on dynamic expressiveness, which is a topic relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data structures (cs.DS).
